160
00:16:57,400 --> 00:16:59,800
<font backgroundcolor="#000000"> Boks z kogutami. </font>

161
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:01,960
<font backgroundcolor="#000000"> Tu nie wolno wchodzić. </font>

162
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:08,120
