<font backgroundcolor="#000000"> Gotowe do walki. </font>

202
00:20:57,760 --> 00:21:01,320
<font backgroundcolor="#000000"> Arena do walk kogutów. </font>

203
00:21:02,080 --> 00:21:08,960
<font backgroundcolor="#000000"> Tak jak arena do korridy, arena </font>
